detail.name: Vegeta (Mini) : DA
detail.effect:
[When Attacking] Draw 1 card.
[Awaken] (Can be activated during [Activate Main/Battle] if the conditions are met.) When your life is at 4 or less, draw 1 card. Then, flip this card over.

[Activate Main][Once per turn](1)(Switch the specified number of energy to Rest Mode) : Choose up to 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards with a cost of 1 or less and place it at the bottom of its owner's deck.
